channel.title: Making portals teleport?
channel.description: Trisidia V3 client/cache/source. I want to make this portal (code 2470) teleport me to the next floor of dung, and I know how to make it teleport, the only problem is that when I click on the portal (with my char rights 3 acc) I get no actionButton: 91XX so I don't know what case to add the teleport into. Do I need to make an actionButton for this portal or what? HELP PLEASE!
